Pricing to fit your business needs
----------------------------------

Plan options for Salestrekker 2.0 are displayed below

*   ### $89.99
    
    #### user/monthly (+GST)
    
    BROKER SUPPORT
    
    For admin staff and loan processors, without products and calculators
    
    *   FEATURES
    
    *   \- Deal tracking and reporting
    *   \- Task management
    *   \- Partner Portal access
    *   \- Client Portal access
    *   \- Workflow automation
    *   \- Dynamic templates
    *   \- Email to Deal notes
    *   \- Merge documents
    
    *   Customer support
    
    *   \- Business days, 6AM to 10PM AEST
    *   \- Saturday, 8AM to 3PM AEST
    *   \- Via Live chat and email
    *   \- Video tutorials and Knowledge base
    
*   ### $249.99
    
    #### user/monthly (+GST)
    
    PREMIUM BROKER
    
    For mortgage brokers that require products and calculators
    
    *   FEATURES
    
    *   \- BROKER SUPPORT package plus:
    *   \- Broker tools
    *   \- Home Loans
    *   \- Asset Finance
    *   \- Commercial Finance
    *   \- Compliance Documents
    *   \- Quick calculators
    *   \- Lender policy search
    
    *   Customer support
    
    *   \- Business days, 6AM to 10PM AEST
    *   \- Saturday, 8AM to 3PM AEST
    *   \- Via Live chat and email
    *   \- Video tutorials and Knowledge base
    
*   ### $149.99
    
    #### user/monthly (+GST)
    
    PARABROKER
    
    For broker support that require calculators and policy tools
    
    *   FEATURES
    
    *   \- BROKER SUPPORT package plus:
    *   \- Quick calculators
    *   \- Lender policy search
    *   \- Property data & reports
    *   \- Customisable client portal
    *   \- API access
    
    *   Customer support
    
    *   \- Business days, 6AM to 10PM AEST
    *   \- Saturday, 8AM to 3PM AEST
    *   \- Via Live chat and email
    *   \- Video tutorials and Knowledge base
